## ✅ PHASE 16 — Semantic Search / RAG (Embeddings)
**Architecture** ✅ (netlify/functions/embeddings.js)
- POST /v1/embeddings via Kaixu gateway (NOT direct Gemini)
- Gemini text-embedding-004 (768 dimensions)
- taskType: RETRIEVAL_DOCUMENT for indexing, RETRIEVAL_QUERY for search

**16.1 Sync** ✅
- POST { action: 'sync', workspaceId, files: [{path, content}] }
- Chunks files into 800-char overlapping segments
- Embeds in batches of 100 via gateway
- Upserts into file_embeddings (Neon pgvector)
- Removes stale chunks for deleted files
- Max 500 chunks per sync, 20KB per file cap

**16.2 Search** ✅
- GET ?workspaceId=&q=&limit=5
- Embeds query with taskType: RETRIEVAL_QUERY
- Cosine similarity search via pgvector (<=> operator)
- Returns top-k file chunks with similarity score

**Schema** ✅
- file_embeddings: workspace_id, file_path, chunk_index, chunk_text, embedding vector(768), updated_at
- Unique constraint: (workspace_id, file_path, chunk_index)

**Prerequisite:** pgvector extension must be enabled in Neon (see Phase 21)

